dcterms:title: Predicts the Future
dcterms:creator: Plumtree (Carla Gillis, Lynette Gillis)
dcterms:rights: Second studio album by Halifax indie rock band Plumtree, recorded at Idea of East studios. 12 tracks (36:48 min), including 'Scott Pilgrim' (track 10) that directly inspired Bryan Lee O'Malley's graphic novel character name and series.
dcterms:isVersionOf: Scott Pilgrim universe; Canadian Indie Music
